<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />The wicked man has a raised face; he does not seek God.</para>

<para style="q1">He never thinks about God because he does not care at all about him.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />He is secure at all times,</para>

<para style="q1">but your righteous decrees are too high for him;</para>

<para style="q1">he snorts at all his enemies.</para>
